column4: As he jumps up and down on the hood his cohorts get off their bikes and watch. SOMEONE observes an instruction card, before you drive fasten seatbelt, check mirrors, hands on ten and two.
they jump out and run on foot.
SOMEONE nods tearfully. They jump up and slap palms. SOMEONE clutches his bleeding shoulder. SOMEONE massages his own hand.
SOMEONE does some clumsy jump kicks.
Crushing windshields, SOMEONE barrels over several more vehicles, then jumps the center barrier.
Inside the hotel, SOMEONE and SOMEONE jump over the bar and cross the hazy room.
